value.string: Location! Location! Location! Rare 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home on a tropical 3,568 sq ft lot in the Exclusive and Charming Kauhale Mahinahina community. Comprised of 19 homes, this Gated community offers privacy within moments from Restaurants, Farmer Markets, surfing, and world class beaches. It took just 5 days for the last home in this community to go… Live your West Maui dreams now before this one’s gone. VIDEO TOUR: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j74RFN7Qgjg&feature=youtu.be

Location! Location! Location! Rare 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, single family home on 3,466sqft lot in Mahinahina. This well maintained home in the Kauhale Mahinahina gated subdivision of just 19 homes is across the street from the beach, within walking distance to shopping, farmers market, surfing, beach parks and all the resorts from Kahana to Kaanapali. House is centrally located within the subdivision and boasts a spacious lawn with mature plumeria and Cook Pine, fenced patio with Palm trees, PV solar system, central air conditioning and insulated to maximize efficient use of both, ceiling fans in all rooms, and crown molding. New paint inside and outside. This house won't last long. Move in ready! Start enjoying the good life!

Don't miss this incredible home. Enjoy the ocean view from one of your three lanais. Open floor plan. Master suite has upgraded tub and walk in closet. Ideal location. Easy access to shopping and Hwy. Listing Broker and Seller assume no responsibility and make no guarantees, representations, warranties (express, implied or otherwise) as to the availability or accuracy of information contained herein.

Located along the watershed between Napili and Kapalua, this pristine location offers acres of greenery with privacy, and breathtaking ocean and Molokai views. It will be vacant for the Holidays, so please come and check out this magic spot!!Vaulted Ceilings, airy space, excellent Trade Wind circulation blissfully keep this beautiful ocean view home refreshing and, comfortable. The recent upgrades include replacement of the windows throughout, new flooring, refinished bathtub, faucets, lighting, dry wall, new ceiling fans, painted throughout the interior, including the garage, and exterior landing. The third bedroom, which is located downstairs, has been converted to a den, but can certainly be converted back easily. There is an additional loft on the upper floor which could serve as a home office, or guest room. The ocean views from this little lofted space are beautiful!! The electric meters are separate, the water meter is shared. There are NO MAINTENANCE FEES, and each owner is responsible for the maintenance of their own home. The roof has been replaced in the past 10 years. Compare what is out there in West Maui for under $900,000.00. Good income potential!! Home is being "AS IS".

Located at the top of the subdivision in a quiet, corner location with a sunset and a partial ocean view. The home features bamboo and tiled floors, granite kitchen counter tops and stainless steel appliances. Big covered lanais on the first and second level great for indoor, outdoor living. Bright home with lots of windows with the living room, dining area, kitchen and master bedroom on the second level. The two guest bedrooms and a family room are on the first level. Freshly painted, move in ready home. Good cross breeze plus ceiling fans and central A/C to keep the home cool. White fenced backyard with lots of tropical plants. Well maintained home shows pride of ownership.

Looking for an amazing ocean view home in the highly sought after Kahana Ridge community? This is the one! This contemporary quality built steel construction home of 2,352 sq. ft. has 3 bedrooms 3 baths and is located at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac and features commanding views of the ocean and islands of Molokai and Lanai. The master bedroom, living room, entertainment area and kitchen are on the second floor with outstanding ocean views from all rooms. Enjoy watching the unobstructed ocean view sunsets and hump back whales from the large lanai off the living room or the private lanai off the master bedroom. Whale watching at its best! Another added feature of this home is a private spa to relax in. The majority of the homes in the Kahana Ridge are owner occupied so there is a strong sense of community and safety which makes it a perfect place to raise your family or own your dream vacation home. The neighborhood is conveniently located close to world class beaches, shopping, golf and quaint historic Lahainatown. Maui Prep Academy ages kindergarten through 12th grade is just minutes away.

Maluna Kai Estates is located on the ocean side of L. Honoapiilani Rd. in Napili. This gated community consists of only ten homes. Ocean and Moloka'i views and a wide open living space. Custom gourmet kitchen with European cabinetry and Gaggenau appliances, a one year old LG fridge, and lofted storage space. The downstairs den has it's own entrance and can double as a third bedroom with bath. The home has it's own private lanai looking over the swimming pool and pavilion. The association maintains the landscaping, gate, water, sewer, trash, and solar heated pool. Home to be sold in “AS IS” condition. Some square footage is not reflected on the TMK. All information in this listing supplied by sellers and Hawaii Information Service, potential buyers are suggested to verify all information for themselves. No sign on property. Please do not disturb occupants. Seller holds inactive real estate license in the state of Hawaii.

Spectacular Ocean views from this two story home with a large covered lanai and views of the island of Molokai & Lanai. This floor plan features the living, dining, kitchen & Master bedroom on the second level. The master bedroom has an ocean view with a walk-in closet & soaking tub. The rooms are spacious with lots of light and details like crown molding, new carpet and newly painted interior & exterior. New painted garage floor. The kitchen has custom made cherry wood cabinets, granite counter tops plus new Stainless steel appliances. The first level features 9' ceilings with a family room and two guest bedrooms. Tropical landscaping, easy to maintain & enjoy. There is a Community park which is dog friendly.

Awesome ocean views from the living / dining room and lanai. Entertaining is an enjoyment with this open floor plan. There is a bonus room downstairs with a bathroom for the person that needs privacy to study/work or just a place to get away. Tile and hardwood floors make for easy maintenance. Situated in a cul-de-sac, safe for kids. Currently tenant occupied, 48 hrs notice to show please.

The impressive exterior features of this ranch style home includes a monier tile roof, prestigious columns and one of the largest square ft. lots available in this subdivision. Lovely trees and foliage provide a beautiful oasis surrounding the home. All living areas are on one level with no steps throughout the structure. The interior boasts a very desirable open-concept floor plan with surround sound inside and out. Sections of floor to ceiling windows and doors off the lanai allow natural lighting, enticing a bright airy care-free atmosphere, which makes a great space for entertaining. Other features included in this area are matching granite countertops and back splashes with a large island in the kitchen, a home office space and an area for dining. The living area and master suite have nearly 12 ft. ceilings. A French doorway located on one end of this uniquely designed home includes a private, luxurious master suite with a jetted tub and separate glass shower with a large walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms and a bathroom are located on the opposite side of the home. This home boasts a three car garage, separate laundry room and a pantry with plenty of storage. The Seller will include a premium home warranty at closing to the buyers.

EXQUISITE, REMODELED, ONE-STORY. Contemporary updates were made and construction completed in July 2015 from top to bottom. Located in the private, gated community of Kapalani Estates, this convenient one-story home is stunning! Etched Glass front door and side panel adorn the entry of this beautifully maintained home as you walk down the well-manicured entryway. 'Rainshower' glass window panels have replaced jalousies. Self-closing cabinets invite you into the kitchen where there is plenty of beautiful "Polar Ice" granite counter space for the cooks. A muted array of gray and white Italian glass tiles create the back wall splash. The turquoise ocean and Pohaku Park and famous surf spot "S Turns" are visible from the living room, dining area and kitchen. You can see the surf roll in and out and lap on the shore. Automatic sun shade blinds hang in the glass-lined walls of the living room. Polar Ice granite counters are also in the bathrooms with new glass shower enclosures installed with mold-resistant grout. Grey mist porcelain tile floors in living, dining, hall and baths with Taupe colored carpeting in the three bedrooms. Kenmore Elite stainless steel appliances and pendant lights adorn the kitchen. The windows and doors were replaced less than 2 years ago. Large outdoor lanai has a trellis cover for meals and entertaining. A cozy back lanai is off the third bedroom where you can greet the morning with a retractable canopy shade for afternoon enjoyment. Large and comfortable rooms. The Community recreation area has an outdoor shower, BBQ, Large pool and kitchen cabana and tennis court.SO MUCH CONVENIENCE within walking distance of shops, restaurants and services. Maintenance fee is billed and paid quarterly. Maintenance of the Exterior of home and roof is the responsibility of each owner. Telephone and electricity are paid in addition. World famous Kapalua Resort is a few short minutes away as is Ka'anapali Resort to the south and quaint Lahaina town. If you want upscale living and the convenience of a one-story beautifully remodeled home, this is a MUST see!

150 feet to the sand and not in a flood zone!! Wonderful family home on large lot with great direct access to popular family beach in Kahana. Home in great shape and move in ready. Many upgrades including in-ground pool, decking, fencing, kitchen, bathrooms and more. One bedroom and one bathroom are used as a attached cottage. Beachfront living at a fraction of the cost. Easy to show on short notice.

NAPILI'S BRILLIANT STAR! This one of a kind celebrity home with stunning whitewater ocean views and 4,292 sq. ft. of air conditioned luxury is nestled far above the lower road in a totally private, quiet tropical setting. Enjoy viewing year round sunsets (and in winter, whales breaching & surfers riding at 'Little Makaha') from the spacious living & family rooms, pool deck, spa, and even the full sized gym (including sauna). The amazing master bedroom suite features a fireplace, custom bath, high ceilings and spectacular ocean view lanai, plus a separate office with it's own lanai. Hand carved ceiling beams & doors, custom made cabinets with detailed hardware are seen throughout this Southwestern themed home. After you discover the hidden tropical courtyard with waterfall and fruit trees, bridge over the garden, 75 panel solar voltaic system, security system, and architectural details too numerous to mention, you'll agree that this home is a must see!

Stunning oceanfront home in a small, private gated community on one of the greatest stretches of West Maui coastline. The home features maple floors, concrete counters and walls of glass that offer breathtaking views of the ocean with sea turtles and reef fish swimming at your door step. Amazing snorkeling and a easy paddle to the Little Makaha surf spot make this a dream home. There are two large master suites and every room opens to the ocean. A beautiful community saline pool completes the package. Surrounded by oceanfront homes that start at $5,000,000, this is a once in a lifetime chance to own waterfront for a fraction of the cost. The home is offered furnished, and the artwork is negotiable.

Hale Honokeana Cove presents itself as the quintessential Hawaiian oceanfront estate in the boutique gated community of Papaua Place. 3 Bedrooms and 4 Bathrooms with a well thought out floor plan of approximately 3700 square feet allows ample space for families to enjoy the sense of place this property exudes. A rustic rock staircase allows for easy access to the world renowned Honokeana Cove, famous for its phenomenal snorkeling teeming with sea turtles as well as great surf during the winter months. This home underwent a recent extensive renovation in 2014 allowing for impeccable modern finishes and current technology throughout. This home has some of the most amazing white water ocean and bay views that Maui has to offer! Contact a local Realtor to schedule a private showing.

Hidden yet close, precious but guarded... Over a 1/2 acre bordered by over 200 feet of West Maui's spectacular shoreline facing North, South, and West. The Alaeloa Point Residence is Maui's finest retreat resort home: secured behind a private gate, close to Kaanapali, and walking distance to Kapalua. Custom built to melt with the surrounding environment and designed to resemble traditional Hawaiian architecture from the 19th century. This high quality home is built primarily of Cedar, stone, glass and Pearl Harbor coral preserved and meticulously maintained. The smart, open, airy 3-bedroom 4.5-bathroom main home built in 2000, includes a 2-bedroom 1-bathroom detached cottage, heated pool and art studio. Nowhere to go: sit and relax, enjoy the whales, watch the sunsets, and relish the Maui life.
